 <h1 class="heading heading-style-i size-30" property="dc:title">The PowerPoint That Proves It’s Not Obama’s Sequester After All</h1>
 <span class="byline byline-style-a">
 
 <span>by</span>
 <a rel="author" property="foaf:publications" href="/contributors/john-avlon.html">
 John Avlon</a>
 </span>
 
 <time class="timestamp" property="dc:created" datetime="2013-02-20T09:45:00.000Z"
 pubdate="pubdate">Feb 20, 2013 4:45 AM EST
 </time>
 
 
 <div class="dek-body">
 <div class="parsys updated-dek"></div>
 <h2 class='dek'>
 Republicans have taken to calling the deep cuts that could reverse our hard-won economic recovery ‘Obama’s Sequester.’ But a July 2011 PowerPoint obtained by John Avlon shows the opposite may be true.
 </h2>
